07:39:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KY2v4f4A0wU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKY2v4f4A0wU&d=02GaBAoxlhcSD3HkkvnXHsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=95e6489f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KY2v4f4A0wU</a><br />\n<br />\n第一個代言？即係做左3年<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/105309_dc4d89861da876a3fb8154d45d96f0b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F105309_dc4d89861da876a3fb8154d45d96f0b1.png&h=696d470f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dcafdf4ef1f35f1cef2672f6b99207747a32fc5","tid":768194,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T07:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/154459_a540e3b33669d6bedf73f6ad2e65ee80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F154459_a540e3b33669d6bedf73f6ad2e65ee80.jpg&h=3ef2fb44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/154509_2c696c0b44337acb5da1f7fb48690cf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F154509_2c696c0b44337acb5da1f7fb48690cf6.jpg&h=bc8dbf27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10a00b5dadf136349377510c2572f4150dcdd40f","tid":768194,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"arome東海堂一系列別具日系風格的廣告，一直廣獲好評，深受大家喜愛。今年，品牌再獻新猷，有幸邀請日本人氣女藝人 &mdash; 広瀬アリス( 廣瀨愛麗絲 Alice Hirose ) 擔任新代言人，務求給大家煥然一新的感受，同時帶出全新「I Love Alice」⽇本草莓蛋糕及甜品盛宴，為大家送上甜美幸福滋味。<br />\n<br />\n廣瀨愛麗絲簡介<br />\n<br />\n愛麗絲性格活潑好動，閒時最愛打藍球及騎馬。模特兒出身的她，曾任潮流雜誌《Seventeen》的專屬model，後來朝女演員方向發展，並於2015年成功榮登十大活躍年輕女優之一。人氣高企的她，曾演出多家日本品牌的CM包括: グリコ 固力果蘋果乳酪、ビタミン炭酸MATCH ; 以及多部日劇及電影如《妄想女友》、《銀之匙》、《釣魚笨蛋日記》等。她的最新動向就是擔演人氣小說《冰菓》電影版的女主角，注目度極高，可說是當今日本藝能界，一顆迅速冒起而又極具潛質的超新星。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">舊聞：</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ladies.gig.hk/2017/02/東海堂邀請日本人氣女藝人廣瀨愛麗絲為全新代言/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ladies.gig.hk%2F2017%2F02%2F%E6%9D%B1%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%82%E9%82%80%E8%AB%8B%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%A3%E5%A5%B3%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E5%BB%A3%E7%80%A8%E6%84%9B%E9%BA%97%E7%B5%B2%E7%82%BA%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E4%BB%A3%E8%A8%80%2F&d=02GaBAoxlhcSD3HkkvnXHsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=722ea077\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ladies.gig.hk/2017/02/東海堂邀請日本人氣女藝人廣瀨愛麗絲為全新代言/</a>"},{"pid":"4b0e9649831885f1aae936b8746756e8912aa08b","tid":768194,"uid":77092,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9d039f31f7f6cc33184408765adf1cbb38ea000","tid":768194,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵濱邊美波仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n聽過名但又唔係好識 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/205806_43f88381302798b61261eac380058541.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F205806_43f88381302798b61261eac380058541.png&h=7108e4e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"904ea5243929a959d887e453c6816d0ab5e30aac","tid":768194,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:07:06.000Z","msg":"點解諗起東海堂又會諗起代言？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" /> 因為諗起月餅囉<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19